      <title>随着新业务的火爆，阿达尼旗舰店利润猛增 130%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/adani-flagship-s-profit-jumps-130-as-strong-recovery-continues</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿达尼企业有限公司（Adani Enterprises Ltd.）的季度利润增长了一倍多，得益于新业务盈利的增加，这家港口电力集团继续从去年初残酷的卖空者攻击中反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/adani-flagship-s-profit-jumps-130-as-strong-recovery-continues</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 08:46:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
